https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Operation_Good_Guys

Operation Good Guys is a British mockumentary series about an elite police unit's bid to snare one of Britain's most powerful crime lords. 

It was screened on BBC from 1997 to 2000. 

It witnesses, on camera, the total breakdown, professionally and personally, of the Operation Good Guys team. 

Throughout the operation, The 'Good Guys' have an unfortunate habit of embroiling into their calamitous world some of the country's best-known celebrities, from actors and footballers, to TV presenters and even the odd ex-convict.



A laugh track was added for the third series.
And a very very bad laugh track was used
